expression: normalized
---
Run skill optimization from a config file

Usage: fastskill optimize run [OPTIONS] --config <config>

Options:
      --config <config>          Path to optimize config file
      --skills-dir <skills-dir>  Override the skills directory path
      --global                   Use global skills directory (~/.config/fastskill/skills)
      --out-dir <out-dir>        Override the out_dir from the config file
      --resume <resume>          Resume from this run directory instead of starting fresh
  -v, --verbose                  Enable verbose output
  -h, --help                     Print help
  -V, --version                  Print version

Syntax: optimize run --config <path> [--out-dir <dir>] [--resume <run-dir>]
